timelineItems.text: Aaaaaaaaand we’re off in Foxborough! Watch #NEvLA live on @FOXSports1 right this very moment: http://t.co/PZY4H7eYfn http://t.co/uasZ5slNyZ

timelineItems.text: Pouring rain in Foxboro, most stayed home. Revs have the advantage of knowing the turf & no Keane. #NERevs
